  <thead>
    <tr><th>universum.</th><th>ASQ-3 (US)</th><th>EYFS (UK)</th><th>Bildungsplan (DE)</th><th>VASU-2022 (FI)</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Motor</td><td>Gross + Fine Motor</td><td>Physical Development</td><td>Körper &amp; Bewegung</td><td>Kasvan, liikun, kehityn</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Speech</td><td>Communication</td><td>Communication &amp; Language</td><td>Sprache</td><td>Kielten rikas maailma</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Cognition</td><td>Problem Solving</td><td>Understanding the World</td><td>Kognitive Entwicklung</td><td>Tutkin ja toimin ympäristössäni</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Social</td><td>Personal-Social</td><td>PSED (part)</td><td>Soziale Entwicklung</td><td>Minä ja meidän yhteisömme</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Emotions</td><td>ASQ:SE</td><td>PSED (part)</td><td>Emotionale Entwicklung</td><td>Tunnetaidot</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>Unlike Bayley and EYFS, universum. deliberately keeps social interaction and emotions as separate domains — giving the specialist a finer instrument for individualised planning.</p>

<h2>How universum. helps the specialist work across all five domains</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Assessment</strong> — development tests (<a href="https://unvrsm.ru/features">/features</a>) automatically break results into the five domains with age norms;</li>
  <li><strong>Planning</strong> — child-workspace tasks are colour-coded by domain, so it's easy to build a balanced course;</li>
  <li><strong>Reporting</strong> — PPC conclusions and characteristics (<a href="https://unvrsm.ru/for-specialists">/for-specialists</a>) are generated with correct terminology per domain;</li>
  <li><strong>Parents</strong> — in the free parent cabinet (<a href="https://unvrsm.ru/for-parents">/for-parents</a>) progress is shown as a radar chart so families understand what the specialist is working on.</li>
</ul>
<p>Specialist plan — 330 ₽/month, organisation plan — 2,500 ₽/month, parent cabinet — free. See the full <a href="https://unvrsm.ru/pricing">pricing page</a>.</p>

